[thinking] **Considering RestClientCustomizer Impact**
[thinking] 
[thinking] I'm thinking about how the RestClientCustomizer adds an interceptor to all RestClient.Builder beans. However, when I retrieve the builder, if no customizer is applied, the bean gets built by RestClientAutoConfiguration with its own customizers. This seems a bit tricky, as I want to ensure the setup is correct. I really need to make sure that the right customizations are consistently applied to avoid any issues down the line!
[thinking] 
